코드 스타일

Settings(Ctrl + Alt + S)
적용(Ctrl + Alt + L)

Settings > Editor> Code Style > Java

자동 코드 변환 (Save 할때)
Settings > Tools > Actions on Save > Reformat code
 - 예외 설정
  Settings > Editor > Code Style > Formatter > Do not format 패턴 등록

Google Java Style Guide
 https://google.github.io/styleguide/javaguide.html
 다운로드: https://github.com/google/styleguide
  - Intellj: https://github.com/google/styleguide/blob/gh-pages/intellij-java-google-style.xml
 Settings > Scheme > Import Scheme > IntelliJ IDEA code style scheme > intellij-java-google-style.xml
 (Tab size, Indent: 4로 변경)


 
